data.description: Welcome to this charming red cabin which features 3 bedrooms 2 baths. As you walk inside you will find an open floor plan with a stone fireplace  in the living room which is open to the kitchen and dinning area. The kitchen boost new appliances, large island and quartz countertops and it has  also been updated with new plumbing and lighting fixtures. Home features Master bedroom and remodeled master bathroom with vanity and new  plumbing fixtures. Living room and kitchen offers new waterproof vinyl flooring and bedrooms features new carpet. Make this mountain retreat  yours today!
